# Environment Variables
# -----------------

# Database Connection
# ------------------
# Using Vercel naming convention for both local development and production
# For local development, set these to your local PostgreSQL connection strings
POSTGRES_PRISMA_URL="postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/golfbattle?schema=public"
POSTGRES_URL_NON_POOLING="postgresql://postgres:postgres@localhost:5432/golfbattle?schema=public"

# Vercel Deployment
# ----------------
# When deploying to Vercel with Vercel Postgres, these variables will be
# automatically set by Vercel with the correct connection strings.
# You don't need to set them manually in production.

# Additional Vercel Postgres variables (not directly used by Prisma but available)
# POSTGRES_URL="postgres://default:password@host:port/verceldb"
# POSTGRES_USER="default"
# POSTGRES_HOST="host"
# POSTGRES_PASSWORD="password"
# POSTGRES_DATABASE="verceldb"